metadata.description:
Sneakerheads FREE MINT is a collection of 9999 unique NFTs designed by legendary artist and founder Ali Dawood. Over 40 meticulously designed 3D, hand-drawn base models with unrivaled levels of detail - capturing the look, feel, and style of a sneaker like never before.

This is the launchpad for a community and collaboration-based infrastructure that will redefine the world of street-culture in Web3.

Visit our official site : https://sneakerheadsfreemint.com
metadata.name: SNEAKERHEADS FREE #1
